{"tid":360481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林子健被鎖上手銬押往西九龍重案組扣查","createTime":"2017-08-15T10:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T10:29:51.000Z","uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb5d439eca869fc910df12e8a42fb1a28a963c1","tid":360481,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"【17:20更新】林子健於下午約4時50分，由警員帶上警車離開紅磡警署，前往西九龍警察總部。其間林坐在車尾中間位置，雙手被鎖上手銬，亦沒有戴上頭套，任由傳媒拍攝其容貌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【13:55更新】民主黨中央委員會今早開會討論林子健事件，主席胡志偉指現階段不適宜評論林子健被捕一案，待警方完成調查後，民主黨將會全面向公眾交代後續行動。"},{"pid":"bb9c688c0c6c0c035c2977fe2152466251aa93f9","tid":360481,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f23ec679e38ab1e23c3868d75fa9232f562d9c","tid":360481,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170815/large/1502788785_66ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170815%2Flarge%2F1502788785_66ed.jpg&h=0461c8cb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}